description:
You and I are involved in a war – a cosmic conflict for our very soul. In this video, we will learn how to equip ourselves with the armor God – so we can gain the victory and inherit eternal life!

Whether we realize it or not, there is a war raging for our soul. Maybe you have felt it – the temptation to do the very things that you know you shouldn’t. Maybe you have fallen in to the same sin over and over again.

Dear friend, I have a message for you today from God – you can VICTORY! If you make the DECISION to follow God, He will empower you to overcome the world, to gain victory over sin, and to stand as a conqueror!

In order to gain this victory over sin, we must equip ourselves with the armor of God.
